{"tid":1259041,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」民建聯開始怕了 加強蛇齋餅糭攻勢！","createTime":"2019-06-26T11:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T06:17:42.000Z","uid":10426,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c4568981239eb92f04c58f59302aeea62afb56c3","tid":1259041,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"話說小弟係石籬呢啲出哂名多廢老的社區成長，不過幸好當區區議員仲係民主黨揸旗。<br />\n<br />\n不過自從幾年前民建聯派啲所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">靚女社區主任</span></span>之後，民主黨的聲勢每況愈下，連佢地都要搞下蛇齋餅糭留住班廢佬嘅選票，不過幾平都比唔過民建聯阿爺條水喉.....<br />\n<br />\n直到呢排反送中事件，上連登見到有巴打話民建聯加強蛇齋餅糭的攻勢，今日就收到電話話民建聯個社區主任叫佢拎米，仲要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個人派五公斤！</span>[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">又派水樽又盛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證明民建聯已經開始怕因爲送中失去區議會議席，各位巴打要留意屋企人有冇中伏！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awcMuNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawcMuNo.png&h=b39d660b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有呢張證十成十係入左民建聯會！各位巴打記住，米照攞，票唔投！要佢地票債票償！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cb293876b75fd98255559bf3f56839f566cb860b","tid":1259041,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72247ffde89ffe8cfbcaa25e8a4adc5229b45a5d","tid":1259041,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84d5113a1e2b96a1cfac94fe4eb5f1b641e5ce0","tid":1259041,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74d3ee5d5b115112bd24f459ea73d87d12229a3d","tid":1259041,"uid":10426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019